fields.title_en: Proceeding of the regional peer review meeting on the St. Lawrence Estuary Ecosystem Research Initiative: habitats frequently occupied by Beluga whales and the food web responsible for the presence of Rorqual whales in the St. Lawrence Estuary; March 28 - April 1, 2011
